                </svg>
              </div>
              <p>"As I look back on the three-month journey of learning, to be honest, Initially, I did not anticipate that this required Commerce course would provide me with such a memorable and rewarding experience."</p>
              <cite>
                <span class="cite-line"></span>
                COMM401 Student, Fall 2024
              </cite>
            </blockquote>
            <blockquote class="testimonial-card">
              <div class="quote-icon">
